title: Friday Night Funkin' - Senpai but every turn a Different Skin Mod is used
author: PrizMatex
description:
Similar to my last video, I wanted to do every boyfriend turn the skin would change however this song in particular is much more long lasting and tends to always call for a duet which allowed me to squeeze in the best mods I could find. Personally, the Senpai song was hard when it came to finding the mods for it especially Girlfriend. Still I have to admit that I love the unique pixel art and death animation a lot of artist put into these mods, really shows how passionate they are when it comes to their work. Once again I still want people to know that I did use a bot to keep things well sync because I don't intend on hiding that fact since I wanted to make this video as a fun viewing experience while delivering people exposure of new skin mods out there. I find the whole weeb aspect of week 6 to pretty funny and epic since technically I am one myself. Overall, this was fun to make but hard to find decent mods to showcase.

Mods used in this video:
Main Website for these mods comes from GameBanana

localize.description:
类似于我的最后一个视频，我想做每一个男朋友转身的皮肤会改变然而这首歌特别是更持久，往往总是要求二重唱，这让我可以挤进我可以找到最好的修改。个人认为，仙桃这首歌在找修改器的时候很难，尤其是女友。不过我还是得承认，我喜欢很多艺术家在这些mod中投入的独特的像素艺术和死亡动画，真的显示出他们对工作的热情。再一次，我还是想让人们知道，我确实使用了一个机器人来保持东西很好的同步，因为我不打算隐藏这个事实，因为我想把这个视频作为一个有趣的观看体验，同时为人们提供新的皮肤mods的曝光。我发现整个weeb方面的第6周非常有趣和史诗，因为从技术上讲，我是一个自己。总的来说，这很有趣，但很难找到像样的mod来展示。
